data.description: Great 3 Bedroom townhome overlooking Heritage golf course! Sunroom leads to Deck with impeccable views. 1st floor freshly painted! Kitchen features solid surface countertops, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash and breakfast area. Formal Dining room. Family room with fireplace. Spacious Master Bedroom has 2 walk-in closets and nice Bath with dual vanity, garden tub and tiled shower. Don't miss the 3rd floor walk-up attic! Rocking chair front porch. Buyer can join the club to take advantage of all the Heritage amenities: golf, clubhouse, pool, tennis. Minutes to restaurants, shops and convenient to downtown Wake Forest. Living Room and Dining Room photos have been virtually staged
